welcomeSub: A software house dedicated to its clients
serviceSubHeading: Professional development customized for your needs
storyText1: Founded by a student at SDU University in Odense, Denmark, STAIN was born out of a desire to help provide students with relevant practical experience within software development.
storyText2: The founder discovered that many talented students were being overlooked because they were considered a liability or too time-consuming to train. In response, STAIN was founded with the goal of providing these students with opportunities, but also training and the experience they needed to succeed in the tech industry.
storyText3: In addition to providing quality software, STAIN has also made it a priority to support the next generation of tech professionals, both through employment but also plans to have a presence at universities, to cultivate a strong talent pool.
